Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:07.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. I'm not finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:10.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be... the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:13.27,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You? The Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.44,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,I have the ability to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:18.99,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,just how much magical power \None has with these chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:22.20,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,And you have no magic whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:27.21,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been born that way.\NNo wonder you couldn't get a grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.76,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you lack\Neven an ounce of magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:32.03,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,in this world where magic is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:34.63,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,What a priceless find!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.39,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:40.10,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:46.85,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then no matter how hard I try, \NI won't be able to use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:50.47,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone so pathetic existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:53.93,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even be able to find a job, \Nlet alone become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:59.85,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your friend, the great \Ngenius over there, mocks you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:01.91,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.65,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's so amazing that he \Nwas chosen by the four-leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.54,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:13.76,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do a thing in this world. \NJust give up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.72,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You were born a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:19.46,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I try, \Nsome things just can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:28.52,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to give...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:29.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:31.94,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:36.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, it's true that you won't be \Nable to become the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:37.66,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:42.16,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that? Even your little friend \Nis telling you it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:47.58,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm going \Nto become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.00,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:52.84,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's no loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.05,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.14,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:02.23,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.13,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Him? Your rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:06.48,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,This brat who has no \Nmagical power whatsoever?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:11.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not... Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:17.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you had to see me \Nlooking that pathetic, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick this guy's butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A gri... moire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.97,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:46.27,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that Asta \Nwouldn't have been chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:55.27,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's always been that way. \NHe always does the unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:59.23,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He always has before... \Nand he's doing it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:07.04,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King... \Nand protect you and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:12.37,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make everyone even happier! \NSo we can have even nicer things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:15.63,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'm gonna prove to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:17.96,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:22.73,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That even if you're poor... or an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:26.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,you can still become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:52.29,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}The Boys' Promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:56.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.38,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:04.56,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:10.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.45,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.92,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:22.28,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:27.68,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:32.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:38.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:41.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.34,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.68,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:03.30,sign_7118_54_10_Years_Ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}10 Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.79,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.29,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.83,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.18,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.67,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. You're such a crybaby, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.80,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.70,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.82,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back, Yuno! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:37.85,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.86,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.37,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:03.71,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.59,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.69,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Sister Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.65,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an amazing cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:14.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, will you \Nmarry me and cook for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:19.99,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It was Father who baked those. \NWould you like to marry him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:25.36,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're the one I wanna marry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.05,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! Marry me! Marry me! Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.46,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me! Marry me! Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.41,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.21,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:41.92,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sister is, um... a woman of the cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:47.43,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet, Yuno! I won't give up \Nuntil I'm an adult, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.65,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:02.75,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"And then the world was covered \Nin deep, deep darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:06.46,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Just when the demon tried \Nto destroy the world..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.30,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:13.45,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"...a very brave mage appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:19.96,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The brave mage fought the demon \Nto bring the dawn back to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.19,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, he defeated the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:30.72,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The mage's light shone ever so\Nbrightly upon the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.37,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The long, long night had come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.76,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,This was the dawn of our world."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.30,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:49.90,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"And so, the mage was dubbed the \NWizard King and became a legend."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.94,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.43,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"And they all lived happily ever after."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.51,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.76,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King still exists, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.26,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:27.02,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The title of "Wizard King" has been passed\Ndown through many generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:34.27,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,All along, they've been\Nprotecting us with their magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:38.87,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of the Wizard King that\Nthe Clover Kingdom is so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.83,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.99,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Wizard King really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.43,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,He's the most important after the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.73,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.22,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,About what, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:00.51,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... gonna be the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.17,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I just wasn't expecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.81,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:16.03,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he defeated the demon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That means he's super strong!\NAnd that's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.97,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be cool, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:24.93,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:30.69,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I become important...\NIf I become the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:34.38,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to make everyone \Neven happier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:41.05,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to wear nice clothes \Nand eat all the good food you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.98,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make this crappy \Nlittle church huge and amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.77,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Crappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you whatever you want, too, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.11,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.28,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.78,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.09,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.28,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.42,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sister! Marry me—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.91,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,That's a completely different subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:10.45,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:11.30,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.14,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, yet, yet, yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.09,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.51,sign_14821_129_December,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,December
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.61,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:36.30,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it I still can't use magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:40.78,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! I'll hang up the laundry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.08,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So marry m—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:45.65,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:46.95,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mar—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.34,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:48.20,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mar—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.17,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:52.01,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:55.67,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you start crying, too, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:01.93,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Nash... won't stop crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.26,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.02,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.86,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Wizard King, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:17.48,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Making a baby or two stop \Ncrying is a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:22.07,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! There, there! There, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.58,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:31.06,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.54,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.11,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:38.71,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there. I was wondering if one \Nof you would run an errand for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.09,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me! Me! Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.94,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:45.55,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone deliver this to the mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:53.38,flashbacktop,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:51.08,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very important letter, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:53.38,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, could you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.36,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.53,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a very important letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.90,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm hesitant to leave it in Asta's \Nhands, so I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.82,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go see the mayor \Nin the next village over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:08.47,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I have to ask him to spare us some \Nfood to make it through the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:12.12,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands now, we just \Ndon't have enough tatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.49,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:21.66,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No. Father asked me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.88,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.93,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:27.55,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.39,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.93,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Asta. Chop some wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:41.70,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use magic, so at \Nleast do some manual labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:45.59,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Did you even dig up the \Ntatoes you were supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:47.70,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,I dug up the ones for \Ntoday a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.78,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.97,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's going \Nto get chilly tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:08.09,flashback,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! Get out of my shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.26,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.46,flashback,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to drink any more, \Nyou gotta bring some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.65,flashback,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't getting any for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.32,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your stupid \Nbooze anyway, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.89,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.87,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.26,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:40.35,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The snow's getting pretty thick.\NI'll have to be careful not to slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:59.23,flashback,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. Please tell \NFather that I received it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.53,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I will. P-Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.34,flashback,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,It's late, so be careful getting home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.61,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.31,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.69,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's taking an awfully long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.94,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.39,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,And Father isn't back yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.31,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just eat without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.58,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not fair to Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.60,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:13.62,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,My pendant... That's mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:17.28,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna exchange it for some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:18.56,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:26.69,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You miserable little brat. Where do you\Nget off having something this extravagant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.30,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Give it... back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.78,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.15,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.81,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.59,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What do you expect to do \Nto me with magic like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.26,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You want to fight me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.14,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,and die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.95,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.80,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.90,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yuno's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.92,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.41,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.61,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.11,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me with your filthy hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:27.54,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You... stupid little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.10,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:41.47,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.75,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.94,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.17,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.57,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:09.77,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Damn little brat just won't give up.\NWhat the hell's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.67,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:19.82,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.68,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:27.48,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I've got your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.33,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:35.23,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's always done the unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:41.71,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.16,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,That sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.67,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.96,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You little wretch with no magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:06.91,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,He... nullified my magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even without magical powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:31.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:54.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I built up my muscles\Nsince I couldn't use any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:58.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they came in handy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.28,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.75,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:17.14,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. It's all \Nmy fault... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:22.00,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:26.60,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:32.60,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King... \Nand protect you and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:37.89,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make everyone even happier! \NSo we can have even nicer things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:42.21,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'm gonna prove to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.24,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:49.33,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That even if you're poor... or an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:53.37,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,you can still become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.40,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We can?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.71,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.70,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:04.72,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can... if they work hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.39,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:10.39,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me, or even you, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.39,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... never cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.42,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.41,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.00,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:29.66,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the Wizard King, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:34.48,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get stronger, and protect \Nyou and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:38.34,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make everyone happier! \NSo we can have nicer things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:47.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Look, look! I got my own grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:51.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's insanely shabby, but I'm gonna take \Ngood care of it for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:55.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there, there, there. \NThere, there, there, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:55.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:58.58,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,you saved me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:04.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repay you for this someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:06.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:11.31,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.46,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna become the Wizard King, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.29,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.19,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.29,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:21.94,flashbackitalics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You mean {\i1}you{\i0} remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were just making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.65,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in being \Ntoo friendly with my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:39.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're poor, an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:44.19,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,or even us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:49.91,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We can become greater than anyone \Nelse in this world. And to prove that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:53.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,To make Sister and everyone else happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:03.96,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:14.84,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:21.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.31,0:22:29.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:36.28,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:39.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.03,0:22:43.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:51.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:57.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:05.11,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:11.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:16.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:43.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can't use magic,\NI'm going to join the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:46.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:50.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover,{\i0} Page 3: "To the Royal \NCapital of the Clover Kingdom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:55.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 3\N\N{\fs18}To the Royal Capital of the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:53.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
